items.name: case finished
items.desc: The running run loop mode has no sources or timers to process.

items.name: case handledSource
items.desc: A source has been processed. This value is returned only if the run loop was told to run only until a source was processed.

items.name: case stopped
items.desc: CFRunLoopStop(_:) was called on the run loop.

items.name: case timedOut
items.desc: The specified time interval for running the run loop has passed.
